910
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:12,870
Xu Wenwen.

911
00:37:13,111 --> 00:37:13,977
Let's drink.

912
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,111
Song Cong, let's drink.

913
00:37:17,470 --> 00:37:18,310
