917
00:37:33,222 --> 00:37:34,270
How are you feeling?

918
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:35,220
Are you okay?

919
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:36,950
I'm fine.

920
00:37:39,910 --> 00:37:40,430
Song Cong,

921
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:42,140
I want some water.

922
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,100
I have an exam early tomorrow morning.

923
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,060
When you're asleep,

924
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:48,700
I'll go back.

925
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:52,270
Are you leaving?

926
00:37:53,620 --> 00:37:55,100
Can you not go?

927
00:37:56,310 --> 00:37:56,910
I can't.

928
00:37:56,910 --> 00:37:58,622
I've got things to do in the morning.

929
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:00,350
Why can't you stay with me?

930
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:06,020
Song Cong,

931
00:38:07,910 --> 00:38:09,950
do you really like me?

932
00:38:11,220 --> 00:38:12,580
Of course I do.

933
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:14,790
No.

934
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,580
That's not

935
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:18,750
how you like someone at all.

936
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:21,350
You're not the same to me

937
00:38:21,350 --> 00:38:23,060
as you are to Chen Huan'er.

938
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:24,220
What does this have to do

939
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:25,060
with Chen Huan'er?

940
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:26,540
I saw the way

941
00:38:26,540 --> 00:38:28,140
