942
00:38:29,270 --> 00:38:31,140
It's over now, isn't it?

943
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:35,700
Yes.

944
00:38:36,350 --> 00:38:37,700
I liked Chen Huan'er before.

945
00:38:38,270 --> 00:38:39,540
But I also lost myself

946
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,700
because I liked her.

947
00:38:41,155 --> 00:38:42,020
Now I don't think

948
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:43,100
that's the right way to go.

949
00:38:43,390 --> 00:38:44,220
Is it wrong for me

950
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:45,140
to like someone

951
00:38:45,270 --> 00:38:46,750
in a different way?

952
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:47,910
Isn't it true

953
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:48,830
that people grow up?

954
00:38:49,310 --> 00:38:50,870
Why are you so mean to me?

955
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:54,220
So now you think

956
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:55,310
I'm being unreasonable?

957
00:38:56,950 --> 00:38:58,580
I'm not being mean to you.

958
00:39:04,470 --> 00:39:05,140
I've been

959
00:39:05,140 --> 00:39:06,990
doing my best to be good to you,

960
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:09,950
to be worthy of your love.

961
00:39:11,060 --> 00:39:12,220
But now you're telling me

962
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:13,830
that's wrong too.

963
00:39:14,700 --> 00:39:15,700
So what should I do

964
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:16,733
to be right?

965
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:18,830
Okay.

966
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:21,990
You said you shouldn't

967
00:39:22,044 --> 00:39:23,888
change yourself if you like someone.

968
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,540
But it was only after I changed

969
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,700
that you fell in love with me.

970
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,700
Don't you see?

971
00:39:31,310 --> 00:39:32,270
Over the past year,

972
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:34,540
I've been acting the way you like

973
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:35,830
in front of you.

974
00:39:36,790 --> 00:39:38,100
I've never been my true self

975
00:39:38,390 --> 00:39:39,910
in front of you.

976
00:39:44,350 --> 00:39:45,430
Don't you realize that?

977
00:39:45,580 --> 00:39:46,310
What's

978
00:39:46,310 --> 00:39:47,310
the real you like?

979
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:49,350
Would you like

980
00:39:53,060 --> 00:39:54,540
the real me?

981
00:39:55,870 --> 00:39:58,700
Isn't what I've been
seeing the real you?

982
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:06,950
I'll tell you

983
00:40:06,950 --> 00:40:08,470
what the real me is.

984
00:40:09,870 --> 00:40:11,100
The real me...

985
00:40:13,540 --> 00:40:14,310
The real me

986
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:15,430
is the one who claims

987
00:40:15,430 --> 00:40:16,990
to be into literature,

988
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:18,310
but in reality,

989
00:40:18,310 --> 00:40:19,990
I'm on a second-rate fiction site

990
00:40:20,270 --> 00:40:22,470
and I'm just spouting nonsense
for the rewards.

991
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,100
The real me

992
00:40:25,470 --> 00:40:28,100
is the one who says I have to rely
on myself and not on my family,

993
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:29,580
but in fact,

994
00:40:29,688 --> 00:40:30,950
I rely on selling those bags

995
00:40:30,950 --> 00:40:32,350
my mom bought me

996
00:40:32,350 --> 00:40:34,060
to save face.

997
00:40:35,830 --> 00:40:36,950
The real me

998
00:40:37,470 --> 00:40:38,580
is obviously want an

999
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:39,750
equal love,

1000
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:41,620
but

1001
00:40:41,620 --> 00:40:43,620
I am cautious

1002
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:45,870
in an unequal relationship

1003
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:48,580
and lose myself.

1004
00:40:55,790 --> 00:40:57,140
Do you still like

1005
00:40:58,430 --> 00:40:59,220
this vain,

1006
00:41:00,910 --> 00:41:01,990
weak,

1007
00:41:04,950 --> 00:41:06,500
real me?

1008
00:41:15,270 --> 00:41:16,580
Qi Qi, you're not like that.

1009
00:41:17,750 --> 00:41:19,500
The you I know is sensitive

1010
00:41:20,430 --> 00:41:21,100
but has a

1011
00:41:21,100 --> 00:41:22,700
soft, kind heart.

1012
00:41:23,910 --> 00:41:25,500
You've always been the same Qi Qi

1013
00:41:25,533 --> 00:41:26,580
who pursues her dreams,

1014
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:29,310
longs for freedom and is brave.

1015
00:41:33,700 --> 00:41:35,540
But we all have to grow up.

1016
00:41:37,140 --> 00:41:38,470
Isn't that what you said?

1017
00:41:44,700 --> 00:41:45,470
Leave now.

1018
00:41:46,870 --> 00:41:48,220
I don't want to see you right now.

1019
00:41:50,355 --> 00:41:51,540
I just want to be myself

1020
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:52,620
for real.

1021
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:14,830
If I tell you

1022
00:42:16,390 --> 00:42:18,060
that I don't like it when you change me

1023
00:42:18,060 --> 00:42:19,470
into someone I don't like,

1024
00:42:23,580 --> 00:42:25,020
will you still like

1025
00:42:26,350 --> 00:42:27,270
the real me?

1026
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:52,860
♪You're silent in the midst of the lies♪

1027
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:56,020
(We were never)

1028
00:42:56,020 --> 00:42:57,350
(on the same page to begin with.)

1029
00:42:58,910 --> 00:43:00,060
(If I can give her)

1030
00:43:00,430 --> 00:43:02,140
(a better life by working hard,)

1031
00:43:02,180 --> 00:43:04,111
(then I'm willing
to work as hard as I can.)

1032
00:43:04,866 --> 00:43:05,830
(But the truth is)

1033
00:43:06,180 --> 00:43:07,700
(that my pursuit of a career)

1034
00:43:07,700 --> 00:43:09,390
will never match

1035
00:43:09,390 --> 00:43:10,950
the material conditions

1036
00:43:10,950 --> 00:43:12,270
that she's currently living in.

1037
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:15,470
(I thought)

1038
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:18,060
(all two people needed to be together)

1039
00:43:18,088 --> 00:43:19,950
(was to be true to each other.)

1040
00:43:22,470 --> 00:43:23,700
(But now I realize)

1041
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:25,220
(that family,)

1042
00:43:25,870 --> 00:43:26,470
(background,)

1043
00:43:27,580 --> 00:43:28,830
(social circle,)

1044
00:43:29,870 --> 00:43:31,270
(all these gaps)

1045
00:43:32,350 --> 00:43:33,580
(can't be overcome)

1046
00:43:34,470 --> 00:43:35,700
(just by my love.)

1047
00:43:37,300 --> 00:43:40,860
♪Apart from being separated♪

1048
00:43:41,140 --> 00:43:51,660
♪Do we have no other choice?♪

1049
00:44:20,521 --> 00:44:25,691
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

1050
00:44:27,481 --> 00:44:32,561
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

1051
00:44:34,331 --> 00:44:39,681
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

1052
00:44:39,991 --> 00:44:45,481
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

1053
00:44:48,071 --> 00:44:53,091
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

1054
00:44:54,881 --> 00:45:00,121
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

1055
00:45:01,721 --> 00:45:07,141
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

1056
00:45:07,601 --> 00:45:13,101
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

1057
00:45:14,301 --> 00:45:18,261
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

1058
00:45:18,261 --> 00:45:23,251
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

1059
00:45:23,381 --> 00:45:26,811
♪And full of life♪

1060
00:45:28,101 --> 00:45:31,561
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

1061
00:45:31,561 --> 00:45:36,671
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

1062
00:45:36,931 --> 00:45:41,321
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

1063
00:45:41,821 --> 00:45:45,721
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

1064
00:45:45,721 --> 00:45:50,661
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

1065
00:45:50,661 --> 00:45:53,451
♪To know right from wrong♪

1066
00:45:55,361 --> 00:45:58,891
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

1067
00:45:58,891 --> 00:46:02,141
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

1068
00:46:02,301 --> 00:46:08,061
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

1069
00:46:08,481 --> 00:46:13,081
♪At just the right time♪

